# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:12
translate portuguese gertrude7_e4a486c5:

    # "I start talking with Gertrude about the things that have been on my mind the last few days, but very quickly notice that she's not paying attention."
    "Começo a falar com a Gertrude sobre as coisas que me têm andado na cabeça nos últimos dias, mas rapidamente percebo que ela não está a prestar atenção."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:13
translate portuguese gertrude7_97b63e7d:

    # "She seems upset about something."
    "Ela parece chateada com alguma coisa."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:14
translate portuguese gertrude7_aae39d82:

    # pc "Hey, Gertrude? You okay?"
    pc "Ei, Gertrude? Estás bem?"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:16
translate portuguese gertrude7_efec7b50:

    # sc "Sorry, what? I kind of blanked out for a while there."
    sc "Desculpa, o quê? Fiquei meio ausente por um bocado."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:17
translate portuguese gertrude7_482afb8f:

    # pc "Yeah, I noticed. What's going on?"
    pc "Sim, reparei. O que se passa?"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:19
translate portuguese gertrude7_cec5b723:

    # sc "It's just been a bad day."
    sc "Tem sido apenas um dia mau."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:20
translate portuguese gertrude7_e262f6a2:

    # pc "But the day has just started."
    pc "Mas o dia ainda agora começou."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:21
translate portuguese gertrude7_f0bbe887:

    # sc "Yeah, well yesterday was bad too. And the day before. And probably the day before that."
    sc "Sim, bem, ontem também foi mau. E anteontem. E provavelmente no dia anterior a esse."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:22
translate portuguese gertrude7_7ce1ef4f:

    # pc "Sounds rough. Want to talk about it?"
    pc "Parece difícil. Queres falar sobre isso?"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:23
translate portuguese gertrude7_f2ba9b25:

    # sc "I probably shouldn't."
    sc "Provavelmente não devia."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:24
translate portuguese gertrude7_9a6b5393:

    # pc "It's okay. We're friends, remember?"
    pc "Não faz mal. Somos amigas, lembras-te?"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:26
translate portuguese gertrude7_a064582c:

    # sc "Yeah, I guess we are."
    sc "Sim, acho que somos."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:28
translate portuguese gertrude7_c6b054d3:

    # sc "Okay, so my husband is a VP at his company and he has to go away for weeks sometimes. I think we've talked about this before."
    sc "Ok, então o meu marido é vice-presidente na empresa dele e às vezes tem de se ausentar durante semanas. Acho que já falámos sobre isto antes."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:29
translate portuguese gertrude7_abe3824b:

    # pc "Yeah, I remember."
    pc "Sim, lembro-me."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:30
translate portuguese gertrude7_d8c01a95:

    # sc "Well he's been away for two weeks right now. He was supposed to come back today, but he called this morning and told me he was going to be gone another week."
    sc "Bem, ele já está fora há duas semanas. Era suposto ele voltar hoje, mas ligou-me esta manhã e disse-me que ia ficar fora mais uma semana."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:31
translate portuguese gertrude7_f97068f9:

    # pc "Three weeks… that's rough."
    pc "Três semanas… isso é difícil."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:33
translate portuguese gertrude7_114695f1:

    # sc "What's worse is I think I heard another voice in the background when I was talking to him. A woman's voice. Whispering."
    sc "O pior é que acho que ouvi outra voz ao fundo quando estava a falar com ele. Uma voz de mulher. A sussurrar."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:34
translate portuguese gertrude7_78bd9374:

    # pc "Maybe he was just around other people?"
    pc "Talvez ele estivesse apenas rodeado de outras pessoas?"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:35
translate portuguese gertrude7_d199aa10:

    # sc "He told me he was in his hotel room."
    sc "Ele disse-me que estava no quarto do hotel."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:36
translate portuguese gertrude7_f8a26f59:

    # pc "Oof. Maybe it was just the TV?"
    pc "Ufa. Talvez fosse só a televisão?"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:38
translate portuguese gertrude7_c1291f74:

    # sc "Maybe. But I've had a feeling he's been cheating on me for a while. This is just another thing to add to that suspicion."
    sc "Talvez. Mas há algum tempo que tenho a sensação de que ele me tem traído. Isto é só mais uma coisa para reforçar essa suspeita."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:39
translate portuguese gertrude7_df2e8061:

    # pc "Sorry, Gertrude."
    pc "Desculpa, Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:41
translate portuguese gertrude7_bb8360c8:

    # sc "Yeah. I'm not sure what to do."
    sc "Sim. Não sei bem o que fazer."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:43
translate portuguese gertrude7_124214fb:

    # sc "Maybe I'll just find myself a college guy and cheat on him right back."
    sc "Talvez vá procurar um universitário e o traia também."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:47
translate portuguese gertrude7_a472e7bd:

    # sc "I bet you would!"
    sc "Aposto que sim!"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:48
translate portuguese gertrude7_9155355e:

    # sc "You're kind of a player, aren't you?"
    sc "És um pouco mulherengo, não és?"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:49
translate portuguese gertrude7_64b00869:

    # pc "I'm just trying to help you out here."
    pc "Só estou a tentar ajudar-te."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:50
translate portuguese gertrude7_e344197a:

    # sc "Yeah, sure you are."
    sc "Sim, claro que estás."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:52
translate portuguese gertrude7_dee19707:

    # sc "Oh, thanks for that. I needed a laugh."
    sc "Oh, obrigada por isso. Precisava de rir."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:55
translate portuguese gertrude7_1d5aeafb:

    # sc "Thanks, [pcname]."
    sc "Obrigada, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:57
translate portuguese gertrude7_09c5f7bb:

    # sc "I shouldn't though. Two wrongs don't make a right, you know."
    sc "Mas não devia. Dois erros não fazem um acerto, sabes."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:58
translate portuguese gertrude7_990441d4:

    # pc "Yeah. But sometimes, even if it's wrong, it feels right."
    pc "Sim. Mas às vezes, mesmo que seja errado, parece certo."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:60
translate portuguese gertrude7_94da6d28:

    # sc "Yeah, I guess it does."
    sc "Sim, acho que sim."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:63
translate portuguese gertrude7_a0094ffa:

    # sc "Yeah, you're probably right."
    sc "Sim, provavelmente tens razão."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:64
translate portuguese gertrude7_2caddb85:

    # sc "Two wrongs don't make a right, as my mother always said."
    sc "Dois erros não fazem um acerto, como a minha mãe sempre dizia."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:65
translate portuguese gertrude7_14520e38:

    # sc "Even though sometimes doing wrong things feels right."
    sc "Mesmo que, às vezes, fazer coisas erradas pareça certo."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:67
translate portuguese gertrude7_4e6348a3:

    # sc "Anyway, now that you've been my counselor for the morning, you better get to class."
    sc "De qualquer forma, agora que foste a minha conselheira durante a manhã, é melhor ires para a aula."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:68
translate portuguese gertrude7_b1563ec7:

    # pc "Okay, I'll talk to you later."
    pc "Está bem, falamos mais tarde."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:71
translate portuguese gertrude7_98ca816f:

    # "We both stand up, very close to each other. Looking at each other."
    "Ambos nos levantamos, muito próximos um do outro. Olhamos um para o outro."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:74
translate portuguese gertrude7_ac0b2138:

    # "I start to lean in to kiss her."
    "Começo a inclinar-me para a beijar."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:77
translate portuguese gertrude7_951013bf:

    # "But she quickly puts her hand on my shoulder and holds me back, pulling away from me."
    "Mas ela rapidamente coloca a mão no meu ombro e segura-me, afastando-se de mim."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:78
translate portuguese gertrude7_2262058f:

    # sc "You should head to class, [pcname]."
    sc "Deves ir para a aula, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:79
translate portuguese gertrude7_877ec67b:

    # pc "Right. Sorry."
    pc "Certo. Desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:80
translate portuguese gertrude7_cfee34fc:

    # sc "It's okay. I'll see you later, okay?"
    sc "Não faz mal. Vemo-nos mais tarde, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:81
translate portuguese gertrude7_850ead77:

    # pc "Okay. Bye, Gertrude."
    pc "Está bem. Adeus, Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:85
translate portuguese gertrude7_fe8a244e:

    # "I wrap my arms around her and pull her close."
    "Envolvo-a nos meus braços e puxo-a para perto de mim."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:86
translate portuguese gertrude7_03e06438:

    # "At first, she is a little stiff, but she quickly relaxes and returns the hug, pressing herself against me."
    "No início, ela está um pouco rígida, mas rapidamente relaxa e retribui o abraço, pressionando-se contra mim."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:87
translate portuguese gertrude7_b5efc9fe:

    # "We hold each other like that for a little longer than normal for a casual, friendly hug."
    "Ficamos assim abraçados por um pouco mais do que o normal para um abraço casual e amigável."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:88
translate portuguese gertrude7_3abc9c1d:

    # "When I finally start to pull away, she lets go of me reluctantly."
    "Quando finalmente começo a afastar-me, ela solta-me com relutância."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:92
translate portuguese gertrude7_8e28123b:

    # sc "Thanks for that, [pcname]. That was nice. But you better get to class."
    sc "Obrigada por isso, [pcname]. Foi simpático. Mas é melhor ires para a aula."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:93
translate portuguese gertrude7_1070058d:

    # pc "Yeah, okay. Bye, Gertrude."
    pc "Sim, está bem. Adeus, Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:95
translate portuguese gertrude7_0e8f1b03:

    # pc "Well, I better get to class."
    pc "Bem, é melhor ir para a aula."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:96
translate portuguese gertrude7_5c60e9c3:

    # sc "Right. Okay, see you later, [pcname]."
    sc "Certo. Está bem, até logo, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:97
translate portuguese gertrude7_6679f75b:

    # pc "Bye, Gertrude."
    pc "Adeus, Gertrude."

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrude7.rpy:100
translate portuguese gertrude7_d7e41755:

    # "I leave her office and head to class."
    "Saio do gabinete dela e dirijo-me para a aula."

